title: Lesbian Love is Not Blind
itunes:title: Lesbian Love is Not Blind
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha is down for an adults-only kids party. Kate wants a lesbian version of “Love Is Blind”. They also share some highlights from this season’s “The L Word” wrap party. But not too much. 

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod
